scenes.description: Nerissa Ravencroft introduces her 3D room and looks for her cat on the bed.
Nerissa welcomes her viewers, mentions her birthday, and performs a self-introduction.
Nerissa invites her friends from Hololive English -Advent- into her room to celebrate.
Nerissa shows off the bed area of her room, including her plushies and cat.
Nerissa highlights the vanity area and various Advent-themed references hidden in her room.
Nerissa explains a special 'blind date' game she has prepared for the stream.
Nerissa sends her friends to the corner while she sets up the props for the game.
The prop setup is revealed: a leather chair and a pole in the middle of the room.
